All Implemented Interfaces:
EuclidConstants
public class IntSquareMatrix
extends IntMatrix

square matrix class IntSquareMatrix represents a square m-x-m matrix. The basic matrix algebra for square matrices is represented here Check out the exciting member functions, which are supported by Exceptions where appropriate. (NB. No attempt has been made to provide numerical robustness and inversion, diagonalisation, etc are as you find them.)

Author:
(C) P. Murray-Rust, 1996
